      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im working on a sociology paper for class and i need help. the prompt is basically about how wealth redistribution could be used to fix racial inequality. can u help me write a really strong, persuasive argument for that side? i want it to sound really convincing and hit all the main points.",
